title: Whispered Folktales by the Fireplace
description: Welcome to episode 242 of Sleep and Relax ASMR! Today we'll be reading various North American folktales including: Babe the Blue Ox, The First Tears, Frozen Flames, and Rainbow Crow. Enjoy!
